---
import { ExternalLink, Map, Mail, Rocket, ShieldCheck, ThumbsUp, User } from '@lucide/astro';
import { links } from '../../config';
---

<section class="px-5 py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[60rem]">
    <p class="text-primary mb-3 text-xs font-medium tracking-wider uppercase">Who built this</p>

    <h2 class="mb-6 max-w-2xl text-3xl font-medium tracking-normal text-balance sm:text-4xl">
      Built by a small team, used every day.
    </h2>

    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-12 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed font-light sm:text-lg sm:leading-relaxed">
      We got tired of products that were either bloated with features we would never use or so basic they could not
      handle real life. So we built the one we wanted, and we use it every day to run our own work.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-10 gap-y-10 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <div class="bg-primary/10 mb-3 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg">
          <User size={20} stroke-width={1.5} class="text-primary" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold tracking-tight">Lean team</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
          A small group, no investor pressure. Every decision is made for the people using the product.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-emerald-600/10">
          <ThumbsUp size={20} stroke-width={1.5} class="text-emerald-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold tracking-tight">Used by its makers</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
          We run our own work on Acme every day, so the rough edges get sanded down fast.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-sky-500/10">
          <Mail size={20} stroke-width={1.5} class="text-sky-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold tracking-tight">Direct support</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
          Every email lands in our inbox. No ticket queues, no chatbots in between.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-violet-500/10">
          <Map size={20} stroke-width={1.5} class="text-violet-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold tracking-tight">
          <a
            href={links.feedback}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 hover:underline"
          >
            Public roadmap
            <ExternalLink size={12} />
          </a>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
          Request features, vote on ideas, and follow what is shipping in the open.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-rose-500/10">
          <ShieldCheck size={20} stroke-width={1.5} class="text-rose-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold tracking-tight">No data resale</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
          Your data is your business. Acme never sells your data to anyone, ever.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="mb-3 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-amber-500/10">
          <Rocket size={20} stroke-width={1.5} class="text-amber-600" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold tracking-tight">Ships often</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
          Small updates land most weeks. New features ship every month. Nothing sits in committee.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
